    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chains, often decorative, attached to a watch or other item which is carried in the fob pocket. They may also be attached to a decorative ornamental object, the fob.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
